column5: Thank you! Have been looking around for a new game to download. Definitely a great timing.
Where do I find night market submarine?

I tried so hard to fight the feeling of not being able to do anything. Almost died 4 years ago because of this. The thoughts slowly creeps here and there but I am now also at the functional depression stage. Tried medication, did not work well. Any suggestions to get through this without meds?
